<section id="sobre-mi" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    
    <!-- Visual block -->
    <div class="order-2 md:order-1 relative w-full max-w-sm mx-auto md:max-w-none aspect-square bg-brand-light rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center p-8 group overflow-hidden">
       <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-brand-accent/10 to-transparent z-10 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-700"></div>
       <div class="z-20 text-center">
         <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-xl bg-brand-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-accent">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.362 5.214A8.252 8.252 0 0112 21 8.25 8.25 0 016.038 7.048 8.287 8.287 0 009 9.6a8.983 8.983 0 013.361-6.867 8.21 8.21 0 003 2.48z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18a3.75 3.75 0 00.495-7.467 5.99 5.99 0 00-1.925 3.546 5.974 5.974 0 01-2.133-1A3.75 3.75 0 0012 18z" />
            </svg>
         </div>
         <p class="text-2xl font-serif text-brand-primary font-medium italic">"El juego es el trabajo del niño."</p>
         <p class="text-brand-primary/50 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-4">Maria Montessori</p>
       </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="order-1 md:order-2 space-y-8 md:pl-8">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-accent font-bold mb-4">Sobre Mí</h2>
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-brand-primary leading-tight">Conóceme un poco más...</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-brand-primary/70 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
        Mi objetivo no es solo dar terapia, sino brindar <strong>soluciones reales y tranquilidad</strong> a tu familia. Con experiencia clínica trabajando con niños y adolescentes, me enfoco en crear un entorno donde cada niño se sienta libre y seguro.
      </p>
      <p class="text-brand-primary/70 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
        Creo firmemente en la colaboración con los padres. Juntos, desarrollaremos estrategias eficaces y personalizadas que fomentan un crecimiento saludable, la resiliencia y una autoestima inquebrantable.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-6 border-t border-brand-primary/10">
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-center text-brand-primary font-medium text-sm md:text-base tracking-wide">
            <span class="p-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-accent/10 mr-4">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            Evaluaciones Clínicas Especializadas
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-brand-primary font-medium text-sm md:text-base tracking-wide">
             <span class="p-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-accent/10 mr-4">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            Terapia Infantil y Adolescente
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-brand-primary font-medium text-sm md:text-base tracking-wide">
             <span class="p-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-accent/10 mr-4">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            Orientación a Padres Exclusiva
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
